title: Chris Hansen from No Sleep Records
itunes:title: Chris Hansen from No Sleep Records
description:
This episode brought to you by Animal Style Records, we have Chris Hansen from No Sleep Records as our guest reviewing the new Darkest Hour, Defeater and Radiohead as well as the movie Hall Pass. We also preview the new Former Thieves record.
